Hey you guys,
is there something wrong?

35
00:03:34,833 --> 00:03:37,166
No! Nothing at all!
Nothing at all!

36
00:03:38,958 --> 00:03:40,291
What was that about?!

37
00:03:40,375 --> 00:03:43,333
Don't ask me. I guess it
was someone's idea of a joke.

38
00:03:43,416 --> 00:03:46,041
Ugh, now I can't get
that image out of my head!

39
00:03:47,041 --> 00:03:49,208
Okay. Shake it off.
On to the next one.

40
00:03:49,291 --> 00:03:53,875
Un, deux, trois... Un, deux,
