69
00:05:15,541 --> 00:05:17,666
Wow, who do you suppose
came up with that one?

70
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:21,208
Well, maybe it was Saeko,
she gets carried away.

71
00:05:21,291 --> 00:05:23,291
And she's kind
of dark, you know?

72
00:05:23,375 --> 00:05:24,916
All right, then, moving on...

73
00:05:34,041 --> 00:05:36,291
Can I help you... hm?

74
00:05:38,666 --> 00:05:41,416
Yes... um... one bowl of...

75
