your cheapest soba noodles.

76
00:05:44,458 --> 00:05:47,708
Wait a sec, you were part of the
Sawachika Trust, weren't you?

77
00:05:47,791 --> 00:05:50,250
That seems like
another lifetime ago...

78
00:05:50,333 --> 00:05:51,750
