79
00:05:51,833 --> 00:05:54,875
and now I'm living this
life of abject poverty.

80
00:05:54,958 --> 00:05:57,166
How many lives did
your company destroy

81
00:05:57,250 --> 00:06:00,000
with its evil business
practices? Hm?

82
